{"tid":2358144,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【林建名病逝】與細51歲何天兒爺孫戀最轟動 曾歷三段婚姻認有逾千性伴","createTime":"2021-01-08T02:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T03:25:38.000Z","uid":212249,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b8cb9c1b51a20bb38ea2fd1cc37827c74c273084","tid":2358144,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210108/_2021010809352486140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210108%2F_2021010809352486140.jpg&h=1a830694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n富商林建名淋巴癌病逝，享年84歲。林建名生前有三段婚姻，均離婚收場，最觸目莫過於2014年跟年輕51年的何天兒（前名何傲兒）譜爺孫戀，戀情爆出後何天兒曾一度不接林建名電話，令林十分傷心。林得悉何搭上西貢地王之子周子揚時再度流淚。<br />\n<br />\n「大少」向來風流倜儻，身邊女伴有如走馬燈，曾認有逾千性伴侶，包括17歲巴黎失身、丹麥「三人行」、飛鵝山車震等，直認不諱。"},{"pid":"d5d7f15b13ad7730d67096e003d3c0e507ba4fed","tid":2358144,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1970253\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1970253&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=3194d655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1970253</a>"},{"pid":"b34a61bcddbb167c4da81a0e347e088caf317110","tid":2358144,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:32:15.000Z","msg":"何傲兒而家去左卜尸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719efa751a0e5dd5cac748f9217226a842695bbe","tid":2358144,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"成世風流左咁耐, 賺左啦, 上天堂有72個處女"},{"pid":"ad12fa2c5d22a1156fdd112